We live in completely different countries and have never met, but I’d trust her with my life. We both have the same dream of moving to Nashville and writing music. She’s an absolute sweetheart. summary: I was just scrolling through Instagram, and I was like, ‘What? Is that real?’ And I checked and it’s real. It’s Taylor Swift Day...
caption: I was just scrolling through Instagram, and I was like, ‘What? Is that real?’ And I checked and it’s real. It’s Taylor Swift Day today in the state of Minnesota! I’m not quite sure what that means for me. I don’t know if I get any extra privileges in the state of Minnesota today. But I do know that the main thing I wanna do on Taylor Swift Day in Minnesota is I wanna play for this beautiful crowd.
